            "title": "Sean Minor Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon",
            "description": "Sean Minor Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon is a deep ruby color with aromas of dark fruit, raspberry,, and black currants. Once in your mouth the wine's silky raspberry fruit flavors and the combination of oak and tannin nuances create a well balanced, rich and full bodied wine that draws you in for more. The soft tannins and sweet oak balance lead to a long and lingering finish.",
