        "pairingText": "Pinot Grigio, Riesling, and Sauvignon Blanc are my top picks for Shrimp. These crisp white wines work well with shrimp prepared in a variety of ways, whether grilled, fried, or in garlic sauce. The Ruffino Il Ducale Pinot Grigio with a 4.4 out of 5 star rating seems like a good match. It costs about 19 dollars per bottle.",
